- 'High-priority' alerts are critical issues that require immediate attention;
- 'Open' status indicates that the alert has not been resolved yet.

- 'actively running' refers to production lines with a status of 'active';
- 'Category 1' is a specific category of products;
- 'average quality score above 80' indicates that the production line consistently meets high-quality standards.

